{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- since English is my mother tongue, I would interpret only into English, from German into English, never from English into German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That would be done by a native German, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that for every language, there would be two-- anyway-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we found we had to substitute, at times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the people that were substituted had to be aware of what was going on before they were brought in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just couldn't be brought in cold from outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had a special room set up outside, or adjacent to the courtroom, with wires into it so that they-- a full team of 12 would be sitting there, listening to what was going on, you see, with their-- with their headphones.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the girls would be knitting, and the guys would be playing chess or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But-- but they-- they could tell, the interpreters could tell, well, so and so is about to get in trouble, and it sounds like I'm going to be called in, you see.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so they would be all primed and set.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if they did get in trouble, see, they'd be ready to step right in with minimum-- minimum delay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "French, German, and Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And English.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that didn't work at all well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians didn't have-- didn't want any non-Soviet to boss any Soviet citizen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so that led to the most incredible difficulties.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wouldn't do what we wanted to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wouldn't-- well, we-- we-- we finally made up our minds that we could barely stand the men, but we liked the Russian girls.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were delightful.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
